=Description=

[http://www.flytecourier.com FlyteCourier] is a technology startup in social-shipping domain. It operates an online marketplace for the fliers to sell their extra luggage space and for the people looking to send stuff to other cities.
The web-based platform (free) provides services like matching, escrow payments using Pay-pal, deal progress/ status using work-flow updates. It also allows people to include services like shopping, pick-up, delivery and customs.


